videos.description: Illinois running back Reggie Corbin breaks through the hole and motors down the field for the 72-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Illinois RB shows off speed in 72-yard TD score

videos.description: Illinois running back Dre Brown breaks free for the Illini's second touchdown run of exactly 72 yards.
videos.headline: Illinois reels off second 72-yard TD of game

videos.description: Illinois wide receiver AJ Bush Jr. catches a short pass, breaks a tackle and is gone for the 67-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Illinois WR breaks tackles en route to TD
